snippet.title: b3agz
snippet.description:
Game related content!!!!11one

On this channel you will find mostly beginner-to-intermediate level tutorials for working with Unity 3D, typically using C#, with something different (but always video game or game-dev related) occasionally sneaking in. This channel is family friendly in language and themes, however the occasional low-poly bunny rabbit may get squashed in the pursuit of game dev shenanigans.

You have been warned.
